The,service,tracks,over,earthquakes,annually,in,and,around,New,Zealand,It,provides,location,and,magnitude,within,minutes,for,over,significant,quakes,felt,across,the,region,each,year,Reporting,stations,detect,events,in,the,southwest,Pacific,Ocean,but,do,not,provide,sufficiently,accurate,readings,so,reports,are,limited,to,events,in,or,closely,adjacent,to,New,Zealand,The,API,accepts,queries,stated,in,QuakeML,a,flavor,of,XML,KML,or,GeoJSON,format,specifying,date,range,location,boundaries,specified,by,latitude,and,longitude,and,magnitude,range,It,returns,matching,reports,by,reporting,station,with,epicenter,location,and,magnitude,data